high_descs: Turn to the left and go around the island to the other side.
Pick up the tomato from the kitchen island.
Turn around completely and head to the right. Then turn left once you reach the wall and go forward. Turn right and then left to face the oven.
Place the tomato in the microwave above the oven. Heat the tomato then take it out.
Turn left then turn right twice to face a black bin.
Place the tomato inside the black bin.
anns.task_desc: Heat a tomato and place in the bin.

high_descs: Turn left and walk past the counter then turn left and walk past the counter and chair then turn left and walk to the middle of the chairs and turn left.
Pick up the tomato that's in front of you on the counter between the chairs.
Walk around the counter island and walk to the stove that's in front of you.
Cook the tomato in the microwave then take it back out and close the door.
Turn left and walk past the counter then turn left and take a step then turn left to face the garbage.
Put the tomato in the garbage.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved tomato in the garbage.

high_descs: Turn left, move around the island to the left, then turn around so you facing the other side of the island.
Pick up the tomato on the island.
Bring the tomato around the right side of the island, to the other side, to the stove, to the microwave above the stove.
Heat the tomato in the microwave.
Bring the heated tomato to the left, around the other side of the island, to the trash can at the end.
Put the heated tomato in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato in the trash can.
